Well, heading is an HTML tag.

00:00:39.140 --> 00:00:42.875
It's used to create
titles and subtitles.

00:00:42.875 --> 00:00:47.630
We have six different
headings from H1 to H6.

00:00:47.630 --> 00:00:49.745
One important thing
about headings

00:00:49.745 --> 00:00:52.055
is that search engines and

00:00:52.055 --> 00:00:54.770
screen readers try to understand

00:00:54.770 --> 00:00:58.235
the content of our website
based on headings.

00:00:58.235 --> 00:01:00.950
So you need to make sure
to use them properly.

00:01:00.950 --> 00:01:03.770
Right now, here I have
two different cards,

