00:01:08.315 --> 00:01:11.195
If I click on this
settings icon,

00:01:11.195 --> 00:01:13.385
I can choose the heading type.

00:01:13.385 --> 00:01:16.205
As you can see, we have
six different headings.

00:01:16.205 --> 00:01:18.620
H1 is the largest one,

00:01:18.620 --> 00:01:21.365
H6 is the smallest one.

00:01:21.365 --> 00:01:24.725
Well, H1 defines the
most important title

00:01:24.725 --> 00:01:26.975
or subtitle on your webpage,

00:01:26.975 --> 00:01:30.815
